				<h3>Discussion of BEPs 17 and 19: HTTP Seeding.</h3>
				<div class="postmsg">
					<p>I prefer the method specified in BEP:19 (GetRight's).<br /><br />Individual pieces can be downloaded placing any scripts on the servers hosting the files, something that isn't always possible (CPU usage should be also considered). Moreover, I guess something like mod_throttle could do a better work at limiting upload speeds.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="postsignature"><hr />Don't mistake your rank and number for superiority. The oldest child may learn from the youngest.</div>
